README:
Title: Model-based fMRI reveals co-existing specific and generalized concept representations

fMRI task with three types of runs: train, imtest, and finest

Train (8 runs): observational training of 2 categories: febbles (category 1) and badoons (category 2) 

Imtest (4 runs): immediate/interim test of category knowledge/generalization to new items

Fintest (4 runs): final test of category knowledge/generalization to new items 

Task order: train_run-1, train_run-2, imtest_run-1, train_run-3, train_run-4,
imtest_run-2, train_run-5, train_run-6, imtest_run-3, train_run-7, train_run-8,
imtest_run-4, fintest_run-1, fintest_run-2, fintest_run-3, fintest_run-4

Information for generating trial-by-trial exemplar and prototype model regressors provided in event.tsv files for imtest and fintest runs.
